Usage: blog [-c config] [option...] <action>

Actions:
  add [post|draft]		Create a new post or draft.
  edit <id>			Edit post <id>.
  ls [id]			List posts, or post [id].
  rm <id>			Delete post <id>.
  update			Update blog.
  push				Publish blog.
  clean				Clean out blog cache.
  regen				Alias of blog clean && blog update.
  help <action>			Display help for <action>.

Options:
  -c <config>			Use an alternate config file.
				(Default is ~/.zblog/zblog.conf)
  -h				Display this help.
